{"tid":1431461,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"唔明白點解連登仔要屌警察，但我支持警察","createTime":"2019-08-08T04:01:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T09:36:46.000Z","uid":23815,"like":48,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"92a598936825fe0416215172732217f984f3a124","tid":1431461,"uid":23815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:01:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">屌你老母啦黑警，你係咪食撚錯屎呀？<br />\n你仲諗住有人會撐你班垃圾？</span></strong></span>　<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n難聽D講，成班毅進仔，要靠個課程要全科合格，你有無羞恥之心？<br />\n你老豆老母供書教學點知個仔弱智既，仲要<span style=\"color: red;\">扮有學識</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">懶係高薪厚職</span>　<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲好意思聲大大去<span style=\"color: red;\">鬧專業人士既判決</span>，話人唔識野，懶有批判思考咁款，<br />\n你個腦係正常既就唔洗去做散仔啦，<br />\n書你班人又唔識讀，下下以家就話好彩無讀ASSO 又盛，話會洗腦<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">收皮啦，你報就有得你讀呀？<br />\n講到ASSO好似好勁咁，你以家D行家咪一大堆ASSO行入去報黑警，<br />\n見唔見撚到佢地幾撚無用呀？<br />\n我三關Interview之後連野都唔想同佢地講就Withdraw左申請啦<br />\n唔好講到做散仔好難入咁先啦</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你有批判性思考、仲有良知既，<br />\n就唔會咁低EQ，唔識同人溝通，剩係同人打爛仔架，<br />\n仲要成班撚屌仲要狗衝到落單比人打，搵媽媽哭訴話市民暴力。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n喂，24K - 36K呢個價唔係反映左你個人真係值呢個價，<br />\n你跳出私人市場搵得返咩？　<br />\n搵唔返，所以你班<span style=\"color: red;\">垃圾</span>先<span style=\"color: red;\">唔resign</span>咋，派比你入就狗衝入去。<br />\n你又要唔夠膽跳出黎，又要話份工點點點，又要話市民點點點。<br />\n屌你老母啦，<span style=\"color: red;\">市民有份出糧比你架</span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">警察係「公僕」，出糧比你果個係你老細，屌你唔撚得架？<br />\n咁唔受得氣既咪撚做囉，垃圾。</span></strong></strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e2c2850973c1efa8b1175280ba9c8864ed2bfff","tid":1431461,"uid":23815,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:02:30.000Z","msg":"利申返先<br />\nDEGREE HOLDER 廢事比班黑警以為我都只係毅進仔"},{"pid":"e9ebf17ba9f9b13320bb44336d4738880ae489d1","tid":1431461,"uid":23815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:03:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94b142845f119d145c0de133808fccfd00d43db0","tid":1431461,"uid":266026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:03:39.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4fd158d4fd60a3b63c8e48480300c306b309337","tid":1431461,"uid":23815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94b142845f119d145c0de133808fccfd00d43db0","tid":1431461,"uid":266026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:03:39.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:04:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支持支持"},{"pid":"fffc22cab68cc0a9831b9276470b1b52bf9fb2bd","tid":1431461,"uid":50658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:05:58.000Z","msg":"屌你啦樓豬<br />\n我支持警察嫁<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係佢地日日做柒事我地邊有更多同路人呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef6180566c2440f9f4e60480530403e16ea37db